    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Clean, honest used car that\u2019s ready to be a dependable daily driver. It\u2019s been cared for and still has plenty of life left, with a comfortable ride and the kind of straightforward usability that makes it easy to own. As you\u2019d expect for its age and condition, it shows some normal wear, but overall it presents well and is a great option for someone who wants solid transportation without overspending. Priced to sell and worth a look.",
      "price": 18950.0,
